{"tid":1378640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷工計劃建議！ 同我推上頂！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:17:35.000Z","uid":63770,"like":81,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"00c9752f762ab703fa680a7a37d146c9d26abd23","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:20.000Z","msg":"首先， 罷工果d日子係一撚定要有集會！係一撚定要有！ 你地個個縮埋係屋企鬼有人知你罷緊工咩， 冇人知就冇人知道個影響有幾大，港豬係要多人陪先會出黎架！<br />\n<br />\n另外， 暫時已知 8月5號會搞大罷工 ， 我地而家開始 要連登開一個集中post , 或者 facebook , 或者聯絡傳媒， 大家罷工既係之前幾日影你地張員工證 upload 上黎比大家睇！  同第一點一樣，人多香港人就會跟！見到有大粒野罷既 更加會鼓勵到大家出黎！<br />\n<br />\n最後， 文宣組 同各位市民 請把握時間宣傳罷工。 罷工係一時 ， 香港玩完就一世 。 衝 衝唔贏 ， 罷工得啦掛 ， 思想上要准備好 ， 罷工唔係1，2日就完事。<br />\n<br />\n只要我地夠齊心， 我地就會贏！ <br />\n<br />\nGod bless HK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7d4a93057ab364e0c25cad090d85c666a58d4e","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:35.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11cbe6df6d9028fece14b2995142ec06c629cf0","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:45.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b216b6f54097160dbf6135bd189f9efe536ea606","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0316c3c5f40487e07d3abb6c0d84fdae1da238a3","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bed3059972b927d15306f69a320b6cf238e94d0","tid":1378640,"