019-07-28T16:23:15.000Z","msg":"７月３０開始啊！罷得成就直接踩到８月５，罷足一星期"},{"pid":"b88ec71c03b79a6e0a5613c709fbfd55bb87653a","tid":1378640,"uid":22967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"不要說 推 試著說 我會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f624afa857f063ab388565c8e44b1482dd89761e","tid":1378640,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15c6eeb6dc4babd862cfe489556535b51cb2b78e","tid":1378640,"uid":209026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7c14c6cd1ae10df46d2830f4195bffe481a49073","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2d77852cae232fd326cc738dea83c171e2b31e","tid":1378640,"uid":151974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"Push!"},{"pid":"5ef71308e9adc6fdbc060f236b6d98e8d8646336","tid":1378640,"uid":118888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"罷工核心：<br />\n由政府公務員AO/EO做主導<br />\n港鐵車長/巴士車長配合<br />\n已令大部份打工仔無車番工<br />\n公務員起帶頭罷工作用<br />\n就算大財團唔跟<br />\n中小企都會動搖<br />\n<br />\n只要人夠多<br />\n佢想炒哂你地？無可能架<br />\n200萬人遊行都試過<br />\n當你有100萬人罷工<br />\n就算罷一日都足夠比勇武衝10日<br />\n來得更有bargainning power<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗喇<br />\n做唔到勇武既你地<br />\n罷工係你爬山既最強支援<br />\n<br />\n多你一個真係好多<br />\n要善用人多既好處<br />\n200萬人遊行無用<br />\n100萬人罷工？點解唔試！"},{"pid":"10f02285e41ffcc00bf0f59c5aff13805bcae288","tid":1378640,"uid":232065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:35.000Z","msg":"香港人太鐘意返工，罷工幾乎要最後最後至做到。<br />\n反而唔好再諗罷工，諗下有乜匿名既野可以做。<br />\n講緊實質野，唔係影證咁簡單。"},{"pid":"ce6aea3eb6e9387cd4db2e94eb9c22115d569dd6","tid":1378640,"uid":16374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"而家係咪firm有兩日罷工？<br />\n分別係 7.30 及 8.5？<br />\n<br />\nFirm就幫手出文宣啦我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e1bd07efae5892e8915af7a3de337d337736ba","tid":1378640,"uid":209026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"022a78ed315ecf9b36b4436d659a64335687baf4","tid":1378640,"uid":57929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"cb276aa37cbf83d86a90c4a116256fd4b209c66d","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"dd8f37411b1c21b9f585e7e6f065c3ebd5b1382e","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:23:57.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"2141c7e8bba61bed89bd7a29d1f4102e9873b105","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"第二點 要靠大家既幫手！"},{"pid":"e1fc974e0f168ef9463731ebdf6f216989ca9c56","tid":1378640,"uid":273095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:22.000Z","msg":"罷硬"},{"pid":"606c2972178f41ac6f1a37be37a8670318a82885","tid":1378640,"uid":276319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"我會罷工"},{"pid":"41b173fa43f10c5a8896b475c46651ea32c76314","tid":1378640,"uid":63770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:39.000Z","msg":"我要罷工"},{"pid":"6e317bd37127436c87a61428af03ee99e305113c","tid":1378640,"uid":262732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"不了，前線醫護人員，唔會咁不負責任<br />\n<br />\n罷還罷，唔好阻到人，逼人罷"},{"pid":"c8e3abd6f25774fafe3dd6c5dadf03b4b9cf9926","tid":1378640,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T1